      "id": 1,
      "text": "Belford first appeared on the map in 1891 when a railroad station and post office opened east of Port Monmouth, marking its birth as a distinct community.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4,
        5,
        12
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
